Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  你把葡萄果酱全部吃光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得千影姐做给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是爱吃也不能吃太多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一直都在强调着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不是和小铃姐一提到红豆大福一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.80,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很喜欢红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也很喜欢烧鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这岛上已经几天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家里一定闹翻天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的要一直在这个岛上生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  那边就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  只有用最后的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这回可要好好完成人工呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  幸亏醒过来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家由于担心雪乃而聚集起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太专注摘葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果脚下打滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不用特意摔到别人的身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家都把雪乃当作自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  要说的话  我就像大家的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真会说好话  小猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我们也会有这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我稍微能有些察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人都听得懂动物的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  一般来说都不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（你不能和动物交谈吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:19.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（读写算是基本哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等等…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  熊熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  刚才还一起摘葡萄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说熊熊肯定会第一个冲出来救雪乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很贪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在附近闲逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  来帮忙寻找熊熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里分为两队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  那样效率会比较高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和行人找这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐和大家去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明显人数很不平衡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,约会啦  约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道约会的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实刚才在这附近还和熊熊在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  稍微注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,淑女的脸受伤了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你自己走不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是脚印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  难道是熊熊的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  只要跟着脚印很快就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  普通都会注意到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是熊熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为熊熊是和我差不多年龄的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和这种大叔完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么看都和熊熊一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是行人一直盯着看才生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这脚印原来是那大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好难分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉食欲很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是和麻知姐一样年龄的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那这家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊的脸更圆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起漂亮系不如说是可爱系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看上去外表很像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但仔细看  就会发觉其实是女生脸的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美少…年？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家无论年龄  脸  外形都完全和熊熊不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然会有那么多熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没有见到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部有弯月牙花纹的熊很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有那么明显的标志的话  为什么不早点说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己几乎都没走过什么路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又被卷入奇怪的事情里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这岛上的女孩子们都是自我主义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正我也习惯这种状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我责骂熊熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为熊熊把做好放置在那的葡萄果酱全部吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就对她说了  「不能成为像小铃姐那样的贪吃鬼」这样过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是过分的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说熊熊  去哪里闹别扭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我是感觉不会因为这么小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你和熊熊的关系最好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在关系好的朋友里是不分一二的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  论交往时间的话  我和熊熊是最长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我还只会玩耍的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃姐她们都已经开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是六岁的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在此以前我一直以为一个人玩是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从和熊熊相遇后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像一开始去捅蜂巢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河里抓鲑鱼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拥有好身材而舒展身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人偷偷一起化妆等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都和熊熊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此后和许多动物的关系也处的很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊转眼就长的比我大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别看她这样  很胆小的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也许迷路了  正为难着  在哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然装作姐姐那样很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实一直都在担心着熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～熊熊去哪里了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然  干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有空哭的话  还不如抓紧去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刺刺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里已经百年不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每天都见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  那边的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不应该在这个世界上存在的邪恶的杀气」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  我就当作是夸奖的话心存感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音就是这样一个傻到脑筋大条的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  都不要出手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和铃之间冤家路窄的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在很忙  等下再陪你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  这居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这连眼睛都无法捕捉到的快速移动的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的动作太多了  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃一直都像这样被大家保护着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸猪排也保护着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  行人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  小猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人他并不是在保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  行人画的好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是发表感叹的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喏  和熊熊很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  请问这只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么突然…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛上是没有男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以第一次看到行人的话  就连熊也会吃惊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衡  这样变装就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问这只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  还以为动物很容易亲近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样打扮的话  不就更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然熊熊生我的气了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  居然这么难找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是离家出走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想找到熊熊就是绝对不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是离家出走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「绝对不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世上绝对没有「绝对不行」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…也许不能说「绝对」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这样想的我  已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己都不相信自己的力量  怎么能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对找出熊熊给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是画的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们的…朋·友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伙·伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这只熊的朋·友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止都还OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我难得画的肖像画都白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问小动物的话  就不会打飞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这画也许不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里有像月牙一样的标志…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是个名叫熊熊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年龄…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪乃一样11岁左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说漂亮系  还不如是可爱系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃  这位大叔说在那边看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个就当作回礼给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…「行行」是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊好像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就在那桥对面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是不是有点太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  行人对高处不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一个人去好了  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  雪乃  跑着是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人把我带到这里了  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  桥塌了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要道谢的话  还早了点吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  倒过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  让人那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到熊熊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很担心  一直寻找着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果是互相在找对方  而迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还一直以为熊熊离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  雪乃  如她所说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  你从刚才就能听懂熊熊的话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  说起来  我能和动物交流了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是习惯这岛的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始行行也是我们的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  不要啦  我才不想习惯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.99,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE7A573}暖和的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:22:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是最亲近的炸猪排的话  还是除了「噗」以外什么都听不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  炸猪排的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也只能听懂「噗」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这回一定要好好地做——人工呼吸！
